title: Duplex for Rent! Available today!
posting_body: ['Nice 2 bedroom duplex unit for rent', '1009 brookdale Rd E Tacoma,WA 98445', '$1900/mo', 'KEY FEATURES', 'Sq Footage: 1,050 sqft.', 'Bedrooms: 2 Bed', 'Bathrooms: 1 Bath', 'Parking: Single Garage with 2 cars in driveway', 'Lease Duration: 1 Year', 'Deposit: $1,500', 'Pets Policy: No pets allowed', 'Laundry: W/D included!', 'Property Type: Duplex', 'DESCRIPTION', '2 bedroom, 1 bath duplex with garage for rent !', 'UPDATED kitchen cabinets, new floors, freshly painted with new bathroom vanity.', 'Good layout and a nice spacious garage.', 'Sliding glass door to the back yard with a private fenced patio.', 'Close to PLU and 512.', 'Land lord will take care of lawn!', 'The rent is $1900/mo.', '$1500 deposit; Deposit is due within 3 days of application acceptance.', 'Garbage and sewer included in rent!', 'Lessee pays Parkland Light and Water.', 'No pets allowed.', 'MINIMUM REQUIREMENTS', '-Income must be 2.5 times rent or $4750/mo', '-12 months of consecutive employment or 6 months in a similar job', '-Credit score of 700', '-Provide rental references from 2 previous landlords(if applicable)', '-Each resident over 18 yrs old must pass a criminal/credit background check', '-NO evictions', '-NO outstanding money owed to a landlord or property management company', '-Proper notice given to current or previous landlords', '-NO SMOKERS', "Please send us your questions with a good contact phone number and a little about yourself and we'll get back to you shortly!"]
